episodes.title: Lori Vallow case: Chandler police interview Lori Vallow Daybell after her ex-husband's death
episodes.description:
Chandler police interview Lori Vallow Daybell after her brother shot her ex-husband Charles Vallow on July 11, 2019. Records released by Chandler police of the 2019 Charles Vallow murder case revealed more details on Lori Vallow Daybell and Chad Daybell's religious fervor that investigators said played a role in his death.

episodes.title: Lori Vallow, mother of missing Idaho kids connected to Arizona arrested in Hawaii
episodes.description:
Two siblings from Idaho, who lived in Arizona for years, have been missing for months and their mother, Lori Vallow, has now been arrested in connection with their disappearance.
